                            <comment id="14283773" author="octo47" created="Tue, 20 Jan 2015 12:30:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Checked more carefully. It seem that offlined SPLIT regions never removed from region states. Merged regions are the same here.&lt;br/&gt;
